*   **[Time zone](/Time_zone):** [UTC+01:00](/UTC%2B01:00) ([CET](/Central_European_Time)). In summer, they shift to [UTC+02:00](/UTC%2B02:00) ([CEST](/Central_European_Summer_Time)), a quaint annual ritual known as [Daylight Saving Time](/Daylight_saving_time) (DST), designed to trick us into thinking we have more daylight.
